title: Sanu, Sanders Traded, Lamar's path to greatness, Early 2020 Mock Draft (Football 10/23)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and Ryan Wilson to discuss the Patriots trading for Mohamed Sanu (2:30) and the 49ers acquiring Emmanuel Sanders (14:30). The guys also analyze Lamar Jackson's improvement and MVP potential in the future (23:30) and Sam Darnold seeing ghosts vs the Patriots (33:30). Will, Brady and Ryan answer 5-star reviews from Apple Podcasts (44:30) and begin to take a look at the 2020 NFL Draft (51:30), debating Joe Burrow vs Tua Tagovailoa at the top.
